<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 19. Gymnopus foliiphilus var. costaricensis. Hymenial elements. A-D Pleurocystidia E-H Basidia. Standard bars = 10 µm. TFB 9750." , "Figure 21. Gymnopus foliiphilus var. costaricensis. Caulocystidia. A Individuals from near stipe apex B Individuals from lower stipe. Standard bar = 20 µm." , "Figure 17. Gymnopus foliiphilus var. costaricensis. A Basidiomata and rhizomorphs B Pileus underside showing lamellar spacing C Pleurocystidia D Basidia E Pileipellis hyphae, showing encrustation and lobose side-branches F Basidiospores. Standard bars: A = 5 mm; B = not to scale; C-E = 20 µm; F = 5 µm. TFB 9750." , "Figure 20. Gymnopus foliiphilus var. costaricensis. Cheilocystidia. A Overview of lamellar edge B-E Individual cheilocystidia. Standard bars = 10 µm. JLM 2221 (USAM)." , "Figure 18. Gymnopus foliiphilus var. costaricensis. Pileipellis elements. A, B Firm-walled hyphae with slime sheath and crust material on exterior of the sheath C-J Diverticulate hyphae with individual lobate outgrowths K, L Extended lobes into ribbon-like proliferations. Standard bars = 10 µm. TFB 9750." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/115079" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/115076" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/115080" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/115077" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/115078" .

